    <title>Asus’ new Zephyrus M16 has a 16:10 screen and Intel Tiger Lake H processor</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="The Asus ROG Zephyrus M16 open, angled slightly to the left on a black background. The screen displays the ROG logo." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/DEYP-K070BvEpKCkWMrefCjSdlM=/0x500:3000x2500/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69267812/M16_04_bk.0.jpg" /&gt;
